Class HpoCase

java.lang.Object
org.monarchinitiative.lirical.core.model.HpoCase
@Deprecated public final class HpoCase extends Object
Deprecated.
use AnalysisData and AnalysisResults instead.
Represents a single case and the HPO terms assigned to the case (patient), as well as the results of the likelihood ratio analysis.
